      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个CampShare投票系统的时序图，核心是展示从发起投票到最终退款的完整流程。首先，Blockchain Gateway作为入口，需要发起投票并编译发送moderator列表。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Blockchain Gateway",
        "CampShare",
        "moderator list"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。CampShare收到moderator列表后，是直接把moderator设置到project上吗？这里涉及到Administrator这个角色吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CampShare",
        "Administrator",
        "moderators",
        "project"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，CampShare会通知Administrator去set moderators to project。然后Administrator需要回查Blockchain Gateway获取最终的moderator列表确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CampShare",
        "Administrator",
        "Blockchain Gateway",
        "moderators",
        "project"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Administrator和Blockchain Gateway之间的双向确认画上了。接下来投票提交的部分怎么设计？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Administrator",
        "Blockchain Gateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "投票提交走AccountManager到CampShare，这里要标注使用FinTech_LedgerService，votes是加密传输的。然后CampShare把votes转给Moderator去decode并commit final votes。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AccountManager",
        "CampShare",
        "FinTech_LedgerService",
        "Moderator",
        "votes",
        "final votes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "加密votes和解码commit的流程清楚了。那如果投票被取消呢？需要画trigger cancel的分支吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moderator",
        "cancel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，在Moderator这边加一条note标注trigger cancel。取消后AccountManager向PLGProject发起退款请求，这次用的是FinTech_AuthVault认证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moderator",
        "cancel",
        "AccountManager",
